<div class="yousay">
  Hi, Iâ€™m calling to ask about getting the COVID vaccine for a person over 65.
  Could I please speak to the pharmacist on duty?
</div>

<div class="instructions">Once you reach the right person, ask</div>
<div class="yousay">
  Are you currently offering COVID-19 vaccines to members of the public?
</div>
<form id="callScriptForm">
  <div id="noOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input class="btn-check" type="radio" id="noNever" data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript" name="yesNoSelect" value="never" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noNever"> Never </label>

    <input class="btn-check" type="radio" id="noPrivate" name="yesNoSelect" value="private" data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noPrivate"> Private facility </label>
    <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="yesNoSelect" data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript" id="noStaffOnly" value="staffOnly" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noStaffOnly"> Only staff </label>

    <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="yesNoSelect" data-hide-on-select="vaccinatingPublicScript" id="noHCWOnly" value="hcwOnly" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-danger" for="noHCWOnly">Only health care workers</label>
  </div>

  <div id="yesOptions" class="btn-group" role="group">
    <input type="radio" name="yesNoSelect" value="Yes" id="yesJustYes" class="btn-check" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesJustYes"> Yes we are </label>
    <input type="radio" id="yesSoon" value="yesSoon" class="btn-check" name="yesNoSelect" />
    <label class="btn btn-outline-success" for="yesSoon"> We will be soon </label>
  </div>

  <div id="vaccinatingPublicScript">
    <div class="yousay">How old do seniors need to be to get vaccinated?</div>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="minAgeSelect" value="65" id="minAge65" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="minAge65"> 65+ </label>
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="minAgeSelect" value="70" id="minAge70" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="minAge70"> 70+ </label>
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="minAgeSelect" value="75" id="minAge75" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="minAge75"> 75+ </label>
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="minAgeSelect" value="80" id="minAge80" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="minAge80"> 80+ </label>
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="minAgeSelect" value="85" id="minAge85" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="minAge85"> 85+ </label>
    </div>
    <div class="yousay">Thanks! Do they need an appointment?</div>

    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentRequired" value="walkinOk" id="apptWalkin" data-hide-on-select="appointmentDetails" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="apptWalkin">Walkins are welcome</label>
      <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentRequired" value="required" id="appointmentRequired" />
      <label class="btn btn-outline-secondary" for="appointmentRequired">Appointment Required</label>
    </div>
    <div id="appointmentDetails">
      <div class="yousay">
        Do you know if you have any appointments available in the next two weeks?
      </div>
      <input type="checkbox" name="appointmentsFull" id="appointmentsFull" />
      <label class="" for="apptointmentsFull" >The schedule is full for the next two weeks</label >
      <div class="yousay">How should they make the appointment?</div>
      <div class="btn-group" role="group">
        <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentMethod" id="appointmentMethodCounty" value="county" />
 	<label for="appointmentMethodCounty" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >County website</label >
        <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentMethod" id="appointmentMethodMyTurn" value="myturn" />
	<label for="appointmentMethodMyTurn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >myturn.ca.gov</label>
        <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentMethod" id="appointmentMethodWeb" data-show-also="appointmentWebsite" value="web" />
	<label for="appointmentMethodWeb" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >web</label >
        <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="appointmentMethod" id="appointmentMethodPhone" data-show-also="appointmentPhone" value="phone" />
	<label for="appointmentMethodPhone" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >phone</label >
        <input class="btn-check" type="radio" name="appointmentMethod" id="appointmentMethodOther" data-show-also="appointmentOtherInstructions" value="other"
        />
	<label for="appointmentMethodOther" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" >Another way</label >
      </div>
      <div id="appointmentMethodDetail">
        <input type="text" id="appointmentPhone" class="form-control hidden" placeholder="Appointment phone number" value="{{locationPhone}}" />
        <input type="text" id="appointmentOtherInstructions" class="form-control hidden" placeholder="Scheduling instructions" />
        <input type="text" id="appointmentWebsite" class="form-control hidden" placeholder="Appointment website" value="{{locationWebsite}}" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="expansions">
      <div class="yousay">
        Are there any other groups you are able to offer vaccines to?
      </div>
        <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="essentialWorkersAccepted" />
	<label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="essentialWorkersAccepted" >Essential workers</label >

        <div class="instructions small secondary">
          If they say anything that's not on the list, mention it in the public
          notes.
        </div>
        <div class="restrictions">
          <div class="yousay">
            Are there limits on who you can accomodate right now?
          </div>
          <div class="">
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="veteransOnly" />
		<label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="veteransOnly" >Veterans only</label >
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="patientsOnly" />
		<label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="patientsOnly" >Current patients only</label >
            <input class="btn-check" type="checkbox" id="countyOnly" />
		<label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="countyOnly" >County residents only</label >
          </div>
          <div class="instructions small secondary">
            If they say anything that's not on the list, mention it in the
            public notes.
          </div>

	<div id="confirmAddress">
          <div class="yousay"> Can you confirm that your address is {{ locationAddress }}</div>
          <div class="instructions"> If that's wrong, <a target="_blank" class="text-muted small" href="https://airtable.com/shrY44NvEjHBscrOH?prefill_Location={{locationId}}&prefill_Type=Incorrect+contact+information" >report an error</a > </div>
        </div>
	</div>
	<div id="requestAddress" class="hidden">
          <div class="yousay">Would you mind telling me what your address is?</div>
          <div class="instructions"><a target="_blank" class="text-muted small" href="https://airtable.com/shrY44NvEjHBscrOH?prefill_Location={{locationId}}&prefill_Type=Incorrect+contact+information" >Request a database update</a > </div>
        </div>
	</div>



      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="yousay">Thanks so much for your time! Have a great day.</div>

    <div>
      <div>Public notes</div>
      <div id="callScriptPublicNotes" class="input form-control form-control-sm" role="textbox" contenteditable > {{ locationPublicNotes }} </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div>Private notes</div>
      <div id="callScriptPrivateNotes" class="input border border-secondary form-control form-control-sm" role="textbox" contenteditable >{{ locationPrivateNotes }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-6 mx-auto row">
      <input
        type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="scoobyRecordCall" value="Send report" />
  </div>
</form>
